    "Details": "The Kouchou is a spiritual successor to the Cicada built for extreme speed and electronic warfare. MASC pushes the 45-ton frame to nearly 173 kph in bursts while a Guardian ECM suite and Beagle Active Probe give it strong situational awareness in both directions. An ER PPC provides long-range harassment capability and a Medium Pulse Laser covers close defense. Word of Blake destroyed the original production line but Wakazashi Enterprises kept it alive.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
